#. type: multicols
#: sections/deckbuilding.tex:256
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"Spell cards\\index{Spell cards} have three possible primary effects.\n"
"Using the topmost, basic version of the Spell usually has no additional costs.\n"
"To access the other effects, you may \\textbf{Empower} a Spell\\index{Empowering Spells} by paying the indicated cost (3) to get a more powerful outcome (4).\n"
"You may pay this cost by playing other cards for their Empower \\svg{empower} effect (e.g. the \\wikilink{statistics/power}{Power} Statistic card) before casting the Spell.\n"
"All Spell cards also have an alternative bottom (5) \\svg{empower} effect.\n"
"You cannot preserve the played \\svg{empower}: casting a Spell consumes all the \\svg{empower} played so far, and if you stop playing cards, the power dissipates.\n"
"You may use a cheaper \\svg{empower} effect than what you've paid for, though.\\par\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"法术牌\\index{法术牌}有三种可能的主要效果。%\n"
"使用最上方的基础版法术通常没有额外费用。%\n"
"要获得其他效果，你可以支付标示的费用（3）来\\textbf{强化}法术\\index{强化法术}，以获得更强大的结果（4）。%\n"
"你可以在施放法术前，打出其他牌来使用其强化\\svg{empower}效果（例如\\wikilink{statistics/power}{魔法威力}属性牌），以支付此费用。%\n"
"所有法术牌还都有一个位于底部的替代\\svg{empower}效果（5）。%\n"
"你无法保留已打出的\\svg{empower}：施放法术会消耗目前打出的所有\\svg{empower}，而且如果你不再打出牌，这些魔法威力也会消散。%\n"
"不过，你也可以使用比你已支付费用更低的\\svg{empower}效果。\\par\n"
"\n"

