#. type: multicols
#: sections/deckbuilding.tex:289
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"Spells can be gained by Building the Mage Guild\\index{Mage Guild}.\n"
"Building it also enables you to use the Spell Book Token\\index{Spell Book Token} for buying additional Spells.\n"
"The Token cannot be used during the \\textbf{same Round} when the Guild is constructed. Spells can also be \\pagelink{Trading}{traded} in Alliance and Cooperative Scenarios.\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"可以通过建造魔法行会\\index{魔法行会}来获得法术。%\n"
"建造它也使你能够使用法术书标记\\index{法术书标记}来购买额外的法术。%\n"
"该标记不能在建造行会的\\textbf{同一轮}中使用。法术在同盟和合作剧本中可以\\pagelink{Trading}{交易}。\n"
"\n"

#. type: multicols
#: sections/deckbuilding.tex:291
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"During Combat, each player may play \\textbf{only one Spell card per Combat Round}.\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"在战斗期间，每位玩家在每个战斗轮次中\\textbf{只能打出一张法术牌}。\n"
"\n"

#. type: multicols
#: sections/deckbuilding.tex:294
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"\\columnbreak\n"
"When you use an effect which lets you cast a Spell from somewhere other than your hand (such as directly from the Spell Deck), place that Spell into your Discard Pile after casting it.\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"\\columnbreak\n"
"当你使用某个效果，使你可以从手牌以外的地方施放一个法术（例如直接从法术牌堆中），在施放后将该法术置入你的弃牌堆。\n"
"\n"

#. type: multicols
#: sections/deckbuilding.tex:296
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"Some complex Spell cards use keywords or require special components, see \\pagelink{spell keywords}{Card Effect Keywords}.\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"一些复杂的法术牌会使用关键词或需要特殊组件，参见\\pagelink{spell keywords}{卡牌效果关键词}。\n"
"\n"

#. type: multicols
#: sections/deckbuilding.tex:302
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"\\begin{center}\n"
"  \\vspace*{\\fill}\n"
"  {\\transparent{0.2}\\includegraphics[width=0.9\\linewidth]{\\art/air_magic.png}}\n"
"  \\vspace*{\\fill}\n"
"\\end{center}\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
