"\n"

#. type: multicols
#: sections/deckbuilding.tex:340
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"\\pagebreak\n"
"\\pagetarget{Specialty}{\\subheader{Hero Specialty Cards}}\n"
"\\index{Hero Specialty card}\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"\\pagebreak\n"
"\\pagetarget{Specialty}{\\subheader{英雄特长牌}}\n"
"\\index{英雄特长牌}\n"
"\n"

#. type: multicols
#: sections/deckbuilding.tex:345
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"Hero Specialty cards\\index{Specialty cards} are gained from \\pagelink{Level}{Level ups}.\n"
"Each Main Hero has a unique set of Specialty cards.\n"
"While some of these cards have effects which resemble Spell cards and even make use of \\svg{empower}, Specialty cards are their \\textbf{own unique category of cards}.\n"
"For example, the limit of 1 Spell per Combat Round doesn't apply to Specialty cards.\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"英雄特长牌\\index{特长牌}可通过\\pagelink{Level}{升级}获得。%\n"
"每位主英雄都有一套独特的特长牌。%\n"
"虽然其中一些牌的效果与法术牌相似，甚至会使用\\svg{empower}，但特长牌是\\textbf{其自身独有的一类牌}。%\n"
"例如，每个战斗轮次限用1张法术的限制不适用于特长牌。\n"
"\n"

#. type: multicols
#: sections/deckbuilding.tex:353
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"{\n"
"    \\medskip\n"
"    \\centering\n"
"    \\includegraphics[width=0.7\\linewidth]{\\cards/specialty.png}\\\\\n"
"    \\medskip\n"
"    \\footnotesize\\textit{A Level IV Specialty card, belonging to Catherine the Knight.}\n"
"}\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"{\n"
"    \\medskip\n"
"    \\centering\n"
"    \\includegraphics[width=0.7\\linewidth]{\\cards/specialty.png}\\\\\n"
"    \\medskip\n"
"    \\footnotesize\\textit{一张IV级特长牌，属于骑士凯瑟琳。}\n"
"}\n"
"\n"

#. type: multicols
#: sections/deckbuilding.tex:361
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"{\n"
"    \\medskip\n"
"    \\centering\n"
"    \\includegraphics[width=0.7\\linewidth]{\\cards/specialty2.png}\\\\\n"
"    \\medskip\n"
"    \\footnotesize\\textit{A Level I Specialty card, belonging to Deemer the Warlock. It uses \\svg{empower}, but does NOT belong to any School of Magic, despite the imagery.}\n"
"}\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"{\n"
"    \\medskip\n"
"    \\centering\n"
"    \\includegraphics[width=0.7\\linewidth]{\\cards/specialty2.png}\\\\\n"
"    \\medskip\n"
"    \\footnotesize\\textit{一张I级特长牌，属于术士迪默。它使用\\svg{empower}，但它并不属于任何魔法学派（忽略图画所示）。}\n"
"}\n"
"\n"

#. type: multicols
#: sections/deckbuilding.tex:364
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"\\columnbreak\n"
"\\pagetarget{Artifact}{\\subheader{Artifact Cards}}\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"\\columnbreak\n"
"\\pagetarget{Artifact}{\\subheader{神器牌}}\n"
"\n"

#. type: multicols
#: sections/deckbuilding.tex:371
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"Artifact cards\\index{Artifact cards} have a top and bottom effect. When you play one, you must \\textbf{choose which effect} you are using.\n"
"They are divided into 3 Levels: Minor, Major, and Relic, with different border color.\n"
"These Levels relate to the overall Power of the card and may be referenced when resolving certain effects or during Scenario setup.\n"
"Otherwise, all Artifact cards are normally shuffled together to form the Artifact Deck regardless of their Level.\n"
"They are gained through map exploration.\\par\n"
"Artifacts can be \\pagelink{Trading}{traded} in Alliance and Cooperative Scenarios.\\par\n"
"\\begin{tikzpicture}\n"
msgstr ""
"神器牌\\index{神器牌}具有顶部和底部效果。当你打出一张时，你必须\\textbf{选择你要使用哪个效果}。%\n"
"神器分为3个等级：次级、高级和圣物，其边框颜色各不相同。%\n"
"这些等级与该牌的整体强度相关，并且在结算某些效果或在剧本准备期间可能会被用到。%\n"
"除此之外，所有神器牌通常都会无视其等级混洗在一起，组成神器牌堆。%\n"
"它们通过地图探索获得。\\par\n"
"神器可以在同盟和合作剧本中\\pagelink{Trading}{交易}。\\par\n"
"\\begin{tikzpicture}\n"

#. type: multicols
#: sections/deckbuilding.tex:391
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"  \\node (major) {\\includegraphics[width=0.6\\linewidth]{\\cards/artifact.png}};\n"
"  \\begin{relcoords}{major}\n"
"    \\draw (0.2, 0.8) node {\\encircle{1}};\n"
"    \\draw (0.7, 0.4) node {\\encircle{2}};\n"
"    \\draw (0.9, 0.9) node {\\encircle{3}};\n"
"    \\draw (0.25, 0.2) node {\\encircle{4}};\n"
"  \\end{relcoords}\n"
"  \\node [below=0pt of major.south] {\\imagecaption{Major Artifact}};\n"
"  \\node (relic) [right=0.05\\linewidth of major.south east, anchor=south west] {\\includegraphics[width=0.3\\linewidth]{\\cards/relic_artifact.png}};\n"
"  \\begin{relcoords}{relic}\n"
"    \\draw (0.5, 0.7) node {\\encircle{3}};\n"
"    \\node [below=0pt of relic.south] {\\imagecaption{Relic Artifact}};\n"
"  \\end{relcoords}\n"
"  \\node (minor) [above=4em of relic.north] {\\includegraphics[width=0.3\\linewidth]{\\cards/minor_artifact.png}};\n"
"  \\begin{relcoords}{minor}\n"
"    \\draw (0.5, 0.7) node {\\encircle{3}};\n"
"    \\node [below=0pt of minor.south] {\\imagecaption{Minor Artifact}};\n"
"  \\end{relcoords}\n"
"\\end{tikzpicture}\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"  \\node (major) {\\includegraphics[width=0.6\\linewidth]{\\cards/artifact.png}};\n"
"  \\begin{relcoords}{major}\n"
"    \\draw (0.2, 0.8) node {\\encircle{1}};\n"
"    \\draw (0.7, 0.4) node {\\encircle{2}};\n"
"    \\draw (0.9, 0.9) node {\\encircle{3}};\n"
"    \\draw (0.25, 0.2) node {\\encircle{4}};\n"
"  \\end{relcoords}\n"
"  \\node [below=0pt of major.south] {\\imagecaption{高级神器}};\n"
"  \\node (relic) [right=0.05\\linewidth of major.south east, anchor=south west] {\\includegraphics[width=0.3\\linewidth]{\\cards/relic_artifact.png}};\n"
"  \\begin{relcoords}{relic}\n"
"    \\draw (0.5, 0.7) node {\\encircle{3}};\n"
"    \\node [below=0pt of relic.south] {\\imagecaption{圣物神器}};\n"
"  \\end{relcoords}\n"
"  \\node (minor) [above=4em of relic.north] {\\includegraphics[width=0.3\\linewidth]{\\cards/minor_artifact.png}};\n"
"  \\begin{relcoords}{minor}\n"
"    \\draw (0.5, 0.7) node {\\encircle{3}};\n"
"    \\node [below=0pt of minor.south] {\\imagecaption{次级神器}};\n"
"  \\end{relcoords}\n"
"\\end{tikzpicture}\n"
"\n"

#. type: multicols
#: sections/deckbuilding.tex:401
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"\\begin{multicols}{2}\n"
"  \\footnotesize\n"
"  \\begin{itemize}\n"
"    \\item[\\textbf{1.}] Name\n"
"    \\item[\\textbf{2.}] Effect\n"
"    \\columnbreak\n"
"    \\item[\\textbf{3.}] Level\n"
"    \\item[\\textbf{4.}] Flavor text\n"
"  \\end{itemize}"
msgstr ""
"\\begin{multicols}{2}\n"
"  \\footnotesize\n"
"  \\begin{itemize}\n"
"    \\item[\\textbf{1.}] 名称\n"
"    \\item[\\textbf{2.}] 效果\n"
"    \\columnbreak\n"
"    \\item[\\textbf{3.}] 等级\n"
"    \\item[\\textbf{4.}] 背景文字\n"
"  \\end{itemize}"

#. type: center
#: sections/deckbuilding.tex:408
msgid ""
"{\\transparent{0.2}\\includegraphics[width=0.9\\linewidth]{\\art/"
"diplomats_ring.png}}"
msgstr ""
"{\\transparent{0.2}\\includegraphics[width=0.9\\linewidth]{\\art/"
"diplomats_ring.png}}"

#. type: expansion
#: sections/deckbuilding.tex:413
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"{stronghold}\n"
"\\pagetarget{Spell Scroll Cards}{\\subheader{Spell Scroll Cards}}\\index{Spell Scroll cards}\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"{stronghold}\n"
"\\pagetarget{Spell Scroll Cards}{\\subheader{法术卷轴牌}}\\index{法术卷轴牌}\n"
"\n"

#. type: expansion
#: sections/deckbuilding.tex:418
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"During setup shuffle 10 of the Spell Scroll cards into the Artifact Deck.\n"
"Set the remaining 10 cards aside to form a Spell Scroll Deck.\n"
"Some locations or Scenario effects may call for them later.\n"
"\\vspace*{1em}\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"在准备时，将10张法术卷轴牌洗入神器牌堆。%\n"
"将剩余的10张牌放在一旁，组成法术卷轴牌堆。%\n"
"某些地点或剧本效果之后可能会要求使用它们。%\n"
"\\vspace*{1em}\n"
"\n"

#. type: expansion
#: sections/deckbuilding.tex:428
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"{\n"
"    \\medskip\n"
"    \\centering\n"
"    \\includegraphics[width=0.7\\linewidth]{\\cards/spell_scroll.png}\\\\\n"
"    \\medskip\n"
"    \\begin{center}\n"
"         \\imagecaption{Spell Scroll card}\n"
"    \\end{center}\n"
"}\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"{\n"
"    \\medskip\n"
"    \\centering\n"
"    \\includegraphics[width=0.7\\linewidth]{\\cards/spell_scroll.png}\\\\\n"
"    \\medskip\n"
"    \\begin{center}\n"
"         \\imagecaption{法术卷轴牌}\n"
"    \\end{center}\n"
"}\n"
"\n"

#. type: expansion
#: sections/deckbuilding.tex:434
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"\\vspace*{1em}\n"
"When you gain a Spell Scroll, place it next to your Hero Board, take the 2 top cards from the Spell Deck and place them face-down on the Spell Scroll.\n"
"You can look at these Spells at any time and they don't count toward your Hand \\svg{hand} Limit.\n"
"You can only have 2 Spell Scrolls at a time.\n"
"If you gain a third one, draw the new Spells normally and then decide whether to discard the newly gained Spell Scroll or replace one you already have (including all Spells on it).\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"\\vspace*{1em}\n"
"当你获得一张法术卷轴时，将它放在你的英雄面板旁边，从法术牌堆顶部拿取2张牌并将其正面朝下放在法术卷轴上。%\n"
"你可以在任何时候查看这些法术，且它们不计入你的手牌\\svg{hand}上限。%\n"
"你同时只能拥有2张法术卷轴。%\n"
"如果你获得第3张，照常抽取新的法术，然后决定是弃置新获得的法术卷轴，还是替换掉你已拥有的一张（包括其上的所有法术）。\n"
"\n"

#. type: expansion
#: sections/deckbuilding.tex:444
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"You can play Spells from a Spell Scroll like any other Spell with the following exceptions:\n"
"\\begin{itemize}\n"
"    \\item They don't count towards your Spell Limit.\n"
"    You can also play a Spell from your hand during this Combat Round.\n"
"    \\item You may use the Spell's \\textbf{lowest Power} \\svg{empower} \\textbf{effect}, without needing to pay its cost (e.g. in case of \\wikilink{spells/implosion}{Implosion} the cost is 1).\n"
"      You can't Empower the Spell with \\svg{empower} from any source.\n"
"\\end{itemize}"
msgstr ""
"你可以像使用任何其他法术一样使用法术卷轴中的法术，但有以下例外：\n"
"\\begin{itemize}\n"
"    \\item 它们不计入你的法术上限。%\n"
"    你仍然可以在此战斗轮次中使用你手中的一张法术牌。\n"
"    \\item 你可以使用该法术的\\textbf{最低魔法威力}\\svg{empower}\\textbf{效果}，无需支付其费用（例如\\wikilink{spells/implosion}{雷鸣爆弹}，费用为1）。%\n"
"      你不能通过任何来源的\\svg{empower}来强化该法术。\n"
"\\end{itemize}"

#. type: expansion
#: sections/deckbuilding.tex:453
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"{stronghold}\n"
"    \\begin{itemize}\n"
"    \\item They can't be used to increase the \\svg{empower} of another Spell.\n"
"    \\item You can \\pagelink{selling Spell Scrolls}{sell Spell Scrolls} at a Trading Post for 2 \\svg{gold} per each Spell on it.\n"
"      This works in addition to other effect of visiting the Trading Post.\n"
"    \\item After using or selling those Spells, the Spell card is \\textbf{removed}, not discarded.\n"
"\\end{itemize}\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"{stronghold}\n"
"    \\begin{itemize}\n"
"    \\item 它们不能用于提升另一张法术的\\svg{empower}。\n"
"    \\item 你可以在贸易站以每张2\\svg{gold}的价格\\pagelink{selling Spell Scrolls}{出售魔法卷轴}。%\n"
"      此效果可与访问贸易站的其他效果叠加生效。\n"
"    \\item 在使用或出售这些法术后，对应的法术牌会被\\textbf{移除}，而不是弃置。\n"
"\\end{itemize}\n"
"\n"

#. type: expansion
#: sections/deckbuilding.tex:455
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"If the last Spell on a Spell Scroll is used or sold, place the Spell Scroll back in its Deck.\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"如果法术卷轴上的最后一张法术被使用或出售，则将该法术卷轴放回其牌堆中。\n"
"\n"

#. type: expansion
#: sections/deckbuilding.tex:458
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"\\medskip\n"
"Spell Scrolls are not part of your Deck, therefore they are not carried over between Scenarios in a Campaign."
msgstr ""
"\\medskip\n"
"法术卷轴不属于你的牌堆，因此在战役中不会在剧本之间保留。"

#. type: expansion
#: sections/deckbuilding.tex:463
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"{rampart,cove}\n"
"  \\pagetarget{War Machines}{\\subheader{War Machine Cards}}\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"{rampart,cove}\n"
"  \\pagetarget{War Machines}{\\subheader{战争机器牌}}\n"
"\n"

#. type: expansion
#: sections/deckbuilding.tex:467
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"  War Machines\\index{War Machine cards} are permanent cards that can be bought at either a \\pagelink{Trading Post}{Trading Post} or a \\pagelink{War Machine Factory}{War Machine Factory}.\n"
"  If you buy one at the Trading Post, \\textbf{you cannot use} any of the other normal functions of that Field during that visit.\n"
"  War machines are also more expensive at the Trading Post.\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""
"  战争机器\\index{战争机器牌}是永久牌，可以在\\pagelink{Trading Post}{贸易站}或\\pagelink{War Machine Factory}{战争机器工厂}购买。%\n"
"  如果你在贸易站购买一张，\\textbf{你不能使用}该格在此次访问期间的任何其他普通功能。%\n"
"  战争机器在贸易站的价格也更高。\n"
"\n"

#. type: expansion
#: sections/deckbuilding.tex:491
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"  {\n"
"    \\bigskip\n"
"    \\centering\n"
"    \\begin{tikzpicture}\n"
"      \\node (card) [inner sep=0] {\\includegraphics[width=0.7\\linewidth]{\\cards/war_machine.png}};\n"
"      \\begin{relcoords}{card}\n"
"        \\draw (0.6, 0.92) node {\\encircle{1}};\n"
